messages.message:
Hey team, a quick update regarding Cypress CI:
Currently, Cypress tests will fail on PR that's > 7 days old because a warning modal "free trial is expiring" will show up. Previously, the run book told people to reach out to me to update the plan in Metronome. Now, you can log into the platform and subscribe to a paid plan yourself by following these steps (https://docs.google.com/document/d/1_YIkXbxu7NE9FD5SQlJs5qj114LD-6yK__-qMA3sWis/edit?tab=t.0#heading=h.inn3ofk1d6qv) in the run book.
I looked into creating a paid commercial org instead of a free trial, but it's quite involved (detail (https://instabase.atlassian.net/browse/CS-5316?focusedCommentId=82788)).
